# restmd request files

Use `AGENTS.md` in this directory as the source of truth for restmd request
structure, validation commands, and agent safety guidance.

- Validate with `restmd check .`.
- Check formatting with `restmd format . --check`.
- Run requests only when execution is intended: `restmd run . --format json`.
- Do not invent secrets, tokens, hosts, or credentials.
- Use `{{name}}` variables with captures, `--var name=value`,
  `RESTMD_VAR_<NAME>`, or frontmatter environments.
